These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, november, august, january, may, july, june
House: ranch-style, palace, farmhouse, wooden, tower, modern, craftsman
 1. the craftsman house is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 3. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the palace house##8
 4. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the modern house##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is not the palace house##6
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 9. the tower house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the palace house##7
10. the palace house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
12. the modern house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
13. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the tower house and the ranch-style house##7
15. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
16. the modern house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
17. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
18. the person who's birthday is in june is the farmhouse house##1
19. the tower house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
20. the person who's birthday is in january is not the modern house##6
21. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
22. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Birthday           | july | august | june | november  | may  | january | september    |
| House   | palace   | ranch-style   | farmhouse   | wooden | tower | craftsman        | modern |

