.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, coffee, sprite, water, soy-milk, fanta
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, pall-mall, cain, alhambra, ritmeester, bongani
 1. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is not the person drinking coffee##6
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the left of the baccarat-smoker##8
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the person drinking coffee##2
 5. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
10. the cain-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the cain-smoker##8
13. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
14. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Beverage   | fanta | sprite | coffee    | hot-chocolate | water | iced-tea | soy-milk |
| Cigar     | baccarat     | ritmeester   | swisher | alhambra | cain       | pall-mall        | bongani      |

