.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, scooter, taxi, ship, quad-bike, airplane
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, coffee, water, juice, 7up
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 2. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 9. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
11. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
13. the person drinking coffee is not the person driving the helicopter##6
14. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
| Transport   | taxi       | ship  | subway | airplane  | helicopter  | quad-bike | scooter  |
| Beverage         | lemonade | iced-tea | hot-chocolate  | coffee | 7up | juice       | water |

