 1. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 2. the owner of the snake is the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is between the owner of the hamster and the person driving the van##2
